f the citizen. No apology was given on the spot and what&rsquo;s more is that he intentionally hit the press who was trying to film the whole incident. This incident has been reported in Hong Kong independent media.  <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Safety is our first priority .&rdquo; is the slogan of your company and it is one of the reason why we, as a passenger is choosing to fly with you. While Flight Operation is highly involved in the safety of the flight ,I don&rsquo;t trust that this kind of management is capable to manage the whole Department and act as a role model to the subordinate pilots .  We all have heard that your company is taking &ldquo;zero-tolerance&rdquo; approach to employees participating in illegal activities.  <br />\nSince Chirs Kempis has obviously suspected in as least three crime, <br />\n1. Reverse driving 2. Negligent driving 3. Common assault <br />\nit is reasonable that Cathay Pacific Airways should treat its management the same as its frontline staff under the same Code of Conduct. Otherwise, It would only portray an image to the public that the Code of Conduct is simply a tool to suppress the frontline staff instead of the real and valid rules. <br />\n<br />\nTherefore, I am asking Cathay to suspend or even consider terminate the employment of Chirs Kempis according to the Code of Conduct and announce the result to the public or I will consider further action including but not limited to organizing boycott and complaining to ICAO ,CAD and FAA.  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBest Regards, <br />\nXXXXXXXXX"},{"pid":"53eac3cec53349de4e526ae1b8a86451e3e7adf8","tid":1531426,"uid":69525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:15:29.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\